snippet.title: Road Defense: Outsiders - Announcement Trailer | Nintendo Switch, PS4, PS5, Xbox One/Series S|X
snippet.description:
Road Defense: Outsiders aims to provide a new experience in the popular action roguelike genre with tower defense elements. Enhance your towers and your own skills to annihilate all life around you. Coming soon to consoles.
